README.md Content
Here's a polished README template you can drop in:
Mini Task Collaboration App
**Full-stack MERN app** with user auth, role-based access, and task management. Built with Node.js, Express, MongoDB, React, and Tailwind CSS.
ğŸš€ Features
- User registration & login (hashed passwords, session auth)
- Admin view & delete any user's task
- Users: create, edit, delete, mark done tasks
- Responsive UI with Tailwind CSS
- Role-based routing for dashboard and admin panel
âš™ï¸ Getting Started
Clone repo
git clone https://github.com/sbbhaskar/mini-task-collaboration-app.git
cd mini-task-collaboration-app
Setup Backend
cd backend
npm install
Add .env with MONGO_URI, SESSION_SECRET
npm run dev
Setup Frontend
cd ../frontend
npm install
npm run dev
Navigate to `http://localhost:5173`
